lead_paragraph: Sevilla midfielder Samir Nasri has returned to training and is a step closer to making his comeback when his team plays at Olympique Lyon in Wednesday's Champions League game, the Spanish club have announced.

headline.print_headline: Sevilla Gets Nasri Boost Ahead of Lyon Game
